412
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:23,800
Right! Right! Right!

413
00:18:31,830 --> 00:18:33,640
Your Excellency Fan, thank you for telling the truth.

414
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:34,760
You're welcome.

415
00:18:34,760 --> 00:18:36,590
Don't worry. His Highness is open-minded.

416
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:37,880
Yes! Yes! Yes!

417
00:18:38,950 --> 00:18:40,920
Your Excellency Fan, something's not right.

418
