567
00:26:58,110 --> 00:27:00,160
After explaining classic texts and
annotating articles for decades,

568
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:01,470
he's got many works to his credit.

569
00:27:08,520 --> 00:27:09,760
In some way,

570
00:27:10,430 --> 00:27:12,230
he's even more powerful than an emperor.

571
00:27:13,350 --> 00:27:16,160
Carrying the literary inheritance all by himself,

572
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:21,640
doesn't he find it burdensome?

573
00:27:22,710 --> 00:27:24,280
If the scholars heard what you just said,

574
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:26,400
you would be accused of disrespect of the saint.

575
00:27:27,350 --> 00:27:28,230
Why would I admit

576
00:27:28,230 --> 00:27:29,280
I said those words?

577
00:27:29,880 --> 00:27:31,400
I heard some people

578
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,800
have anchored their hopes on you,

579
00:27:33,310 --> 00:27:34,800
expecting you to become

580
00:27:34,800 --> 00:27:36,070
a literary giant in future.

581
00:27:37,310 --> 00:27:39,400
Your Highness won't hope so for sure!

582
00:27:42,190 --> 00:27:44,160
Well, since Master Zhuang is here,

583
00:27:44,710 --> 00:27:45,880
the banquet should start soon.

584
00:27:46,190 --> 00:27:47,400
Go back to your seat.

585
00:27:48,350 --> 00:27:50,350
I'll excuse myself.

586
00:27:51,800 --> 00:27:53,760
I've given you the chance,

587
00:27:53,760 --> 00:27:55,280
but you've thrown it away.

588
00:28:22,350 --> 00:28:24,520
Here arrives His Majesty!

589
00:28:27,590 --> 00:28:28,520
This way! This way! This way!

590
00:28:43,310 --> 00:28:47,310
May Your Majesty live ten thousand years!

591
00:28:51,190 --> 00:28:51,950
All rise.

592
00:28:53,280 --> 00:28:54,950
Thank you, Your Majesty!

593
00:29:01,040 --> 00:29:02,800
His Majesty has arrived at the
Hall of Prayer for Good Harvest.

594
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,640
Have you checked

595
00:29:07,190 --> 00:29:09,000
all the maidservants, eunuchs and imperial guards

596
00:29:09,950 --> 00:29:10,760
on shift tonight?

597
00:29:11,190 --> 00:29:11,950
Yes, I have.

598
00:29:12,280 --> 00:29:13,520
All of them have a clean family background.

599
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:14,640
No one is suspicious.

600
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:15,680
Among those who entered the Hall,

601
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:17,310
have you found anyone suspicious?

602
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:18,190
Yes,

603
00:29:19,280 --> 00:29:20,110
Fan Xian is.

604
00:29:20,310 --> 00:29:21,640
According to the Division of Imperial Guards,

605
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:23,040
he carried a dagger and poisons with him

606
00:29:23,230 --> 00:29:25,310
when he arrived.

607
00:29:28,760 --> 00:29:29,800
What about Zhuang Mohan?

608
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:31,000
Zhuang Mohan only took inside

609
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:32,310
a roll of old paper.

610
00:29:32,710 --> 00:29:33,950
My men took the chance to check it.

611
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:35,110
There was nothing inside.

612
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:37,800
In my opinion,

613
00:29:38,110 --> 00:29:39,350
Zhuang Mohan doesn't practice

614
00:29:39,350 --> 00:29:40,310
martial arts.

615
00:29:40,470 --> 00:29:42,920
He wouldn't be a problem.

616
00:29:44,470 --> 00:29:46,710
Yun Zhilan went inside with his sword.

617
00:29:46,950 --> 00:29:47,640
Right.

618
00:29:48,590 --> 00:29:52,070
But Yun Zhilan is an apprentice of Si Gujian.

619
00:29:52,310 --> 00:29:53,310
He is not supposed to

620
00:29:53,590 --> 00:29:55,160
know Zhuang Mohan.

621
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:57,280
If Yun Zhilan tries to

622
00:29:58,560 --> 00:29:59,830
kill His Majesty with his sword,

623
00:29:59,830 --> 00:30:00,680
who can stop him?

624
00:30:01,110 --> 00:30:04,000
Eunuch Hong Sixiang is right outside the Hall.

625
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:08,520
Serve the dishes.

626
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:26,640
Eunuch Hong, it's a night owl.

627
00:30:50,830 --> 00:30:51,710
Young Master Guo.

628
00:31:15,070 --> 00:31:16,040
Chief Musician Fan.

629
00:31:17,830 --> 00:31:19,520
Your Excellency Fan, His Majesty is calling you.

630
00:31:20,950 --> 00:31:21,640
Calling me?

631
00:31:22,230 --> 00:31:23,350
What does His Majesty call me?

632
00:31:23,350 --> 00:31:24,760
You're the Chief Musician of
the Court of Imperial Sacrifices.

633
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:25,760
That's the name of your official position.

634
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:33,560
Your Majesty.

635
00:31:35,040 --> 00:31:38,310
You've seen me a few times, but you've never knelt down.

636
00:31:40,230 --> 00:31:43,310
I thought you would remain standing this time.

637
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:45,640
Then I would piss off everyone.

638
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:59,000
Look at your blurred eyes.

639
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:01,190
You must have drunk a lot.

640
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:03,070
Your Majesty.

641
00:32:03,350 --> 00:32:04,950
On such a big occasion,

642
00:32:05,070 --> 00:32:06,880
I can't help feeling nervous.

643
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:09,470
Yun Zhilan.

644
00:32:11,830 --> 00:32:13,400
Your two apprentices

645
00:32:13,950 --> 00:32:15,640
were killed by him.

646
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:18,400
I know.

647
00:32:18,920 --> 00:32:20,190
Young as he is,

648
00:32:20,590 --> 00:32:21,920
he's somewhat competent.

649
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:30,280
He's competent if he can kill me.

650
00:32:33,520 --> 00:32:35,430
The apprentice of Si Gujian

651
00:32:35,800 --> 00:32:37,760
is really proud.

652
00:32:48,350 --> 00:32:51,710
I get that.

653
00:32:56,310 --> 00:32:57,190
Fan Xian.

654
00:32:58,310 --> 00:33:00,230
According to the memorial submitted
by Court of State Ceremonials,

655
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:02,880
you've done a great job this time.

656
00:33:03,190 --> 00:33:04,710
The war was started because of you,

657
00:33:04,710 --> 00:33:05,560
and it was ended by you.

658
00:33:05,560 --> 00:33:08,470
I don't want to praise you in public.

659
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:11,680
Come on! Join me for a drink.

660
00:33:28,430 --> 00:33:29,680
Chief Musician Fan, please wait.

661
00:33:34,070 --> 00:33:36,400
Your Majesty, I have something to say.

662
00:33:36,800 --> 00:33:37,430
Go ahead.

663
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:39,000
Besides being good at martial arts,

664
00:33:39,110 --> 00:33:40,830
Fan Xian is also famous for literary grace.

665
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:42,310
I'm amazed by his talents

666
00:33:42,310 --> 00:33:43,310
in writing poems.

667
00:33:43,430 --> 00:33:44,470
Recently, I've heard that

668
00:33:44,590 --> 00:33:45,760
when negotiating with Beiqi,

669
00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:47,400
Fan Xian handled it properly without
being too humble or too pushy.

670
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:49,310
He can be entrusted with important tasks.

671
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:51,950
Just go straight to the point.

672
00:33:54,950 --> 00:33:56,680
Why not put Fan Xian in charge of

673
00:33:57,760 --> 00:33:59,920
the imperial examinations next spring?

674
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:01,110
Scholars going down in history

675
00:34:01,190 --> 00:34:03,830
under the supervision of a youth talent,

676
00:34:04,430 --> 00:34:06,280
it might become a much told tale.

677
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:09,710
Though Fan Xian is known for his poems,

678
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:12,670
he is inexperienced after all.

679
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:16,910
Your Majesty.

680
00:34:17,710 --> 00:34:19,040
Though inexperienced,

681
00:34:19,080 --> 00:34:20,120
he is really talented.

682
00:34:20,630 --> 00:34:21,670
I support the suggestion

683
00:34:21,910 --> 00:34:24,360
to put Fan Xian in charge of the imperial
examinations held in spring.

684
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:26,390
Well...

685
00:34:26,390 --> 00:34:27,560
How could this be?

686
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:36,190
There're still a few months
before the imperial examinations.

687
00:34:37,390 --> 00:34:38,630
We'll see by then.

688
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:40,560
Go back to your seats.

689
00:34:44,910 --> 00:34:45,760
Your Majesty.

690
00:34:46,950 --> 00:34:50,120
Is this young man Fan Xian?

691
00:34:50,710 --> 00:34:52,630
Master Zhuang, have you also heard of him?

692
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:54,080
I've read his poem.

693
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:55,840
Young as he is,

694
00:34:56,080 --> 00:34:57,320
he's talented in poetry.

695
00:34:57,840 --> 00:35:00,710
Master Zhuang, you should guide and
support the younger generation.

696
00:35:01,670 --> 00:35:04,630
I'm a minister from Beiqi.

697
00:35:05,870 --> 00:35:09,000
I should not interfere with the political affairs of Nanqing.

698
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:12,040
But the imperial examinations held in spring

699
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,520
are of fundamental importance

700
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:15,950
to scholars around the world.

701
00:35:17,390 --> 00:35:18,870
You should be cautious

702
00:35:19,630 --> 00:35:21,320
when choosing the man in charge.

703
00:35:21,840 --> 00:35:23,230
Master Zhuang, you're absolutely right.

704
00:35:24,230 --> 00:35:25,520
When it comes to the imperial examinations,

705
00:35:26,710 --> 00:35:29,630
we can't be too cautious.

706
00:35:38,870 --> 00:35:40,710
Master Zhuang, I admire you for being
well versed in the learning of

707
00:35:41,560 --> 00:35:42,950
both ancient and modern times,

708
00:35:43,670 --> 00:35:46,760
but I don't agree with what you just said.

709
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:49,760
Though I'm a woman

710
00:35:49,910 --> 00:35:50,870
with little knowledge,

711
00:35:51,470 --> 00:35:53,710
I've read the seven-character poem written by Fan Xian.

712
00:35:54,190 --> 00:35:55,600
He's young indeed,

713
00:35:55,910 --> 00:35:57,280
but this poem alone

714
00:35:57,710 --> 00:35:59,470
can show he's really talented.

715
00:36:00,560 --> 00:36:02,120
What you said just now

716
00:36:02,390 --> 00:36:03,710
is secretly against Fan Xian.

717
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:04,950
Are you afraid that

718
00:36:04,950 --> 00:36:06,630
this young man might surpass you one day

719
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:08,360
and gain a better reputation than you?

720
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:17,150
Everyone else present here is either a trustworthy minister

721
00:36:17,390 --> 00:36:18,760
or a learned scholar.

722
00:36:19,470 --> 00:36:21,000
They certainly don't like to argue.

723
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,600
Ignorant as I am,

724
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:26,360
I'm willing to speak up for

725
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,470
our talent of Nanqing.

726
00:36:29,040 --> 00:36:31,600
Are you referring to that seven-character poem?

727
00:36:32,670 --> 00:36:33,760
Exactly!

728
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:36,950
Master, have you got any poem

729
00:36:36,950 --> 00:36:38,950
better than that?

730
00:36:38,950 --> 00:36:42,190
Yunrui, mind your manners in the Hall.

731
00:36:45,470 --> 00:36:47,000
Master Zhuang, you're broad-minded.

732
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:50,040
Please forgive her for being rude.

733
00:36:55,670 --> 00:36:59,360
The wind so swift, the sky so wide, apes wail and cry;

734
00:36:59,870 --> 00:37:04,760
Water so clear and beach so white, birds wheel and fly.

735
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:07,800
The boundless forest sheds its leaves shower by shower;

736
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:12,840
The endless river rolls its waves hour after hour.

737
00:37:13,630 --> 00:37:17,520
A thousand miles from home,
I'm grieved at autumn's plight;

738
00:37:18,120 --> 00:37:22,120
Ill now and then for years, alone I'm on this height.

739
00:37:23,360 --> 00:37:27,600
Living in times so hard, at frosted hair I pine;

740
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:34,950
Cast down by poverty, I have to give up wine.

741
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:39,630
What a fantastic poem!

742
00:37:40,430 --> 00:37:41,910
I've written poems my whole life,

743
00:37:42,080 --> 00:37:43,320
but none

744
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:45,470
can match that.

745
00:37:46,520 --> 00:37:47,360
So Master Zhuang,

746
00:37:47,710 --> 00:37:49,800
you admit defeat candidly.

747
00:37:50,520 --> 00:37:53,000
The first four lines are wonderful.

748
00:37:53,560 --> 00:37:54,760
But people all say

749
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:56,870
the essence of the poem

750
00:37:56,870 --> 00:37:57,910
is the latter four lines.

751
00:37:58,280 --> 00:38:01,120
The latter four lines are absolutely marvelous.

752
00:38:03,430 --> 00:38:04,360
But unfortunately,

753
00:38:06,600 --> 00:38:08,840
they were not written by Mr. Fan.

754
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:11,760
So Fan Xian copied the poem.

755
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,040
Yes.

756
00:38:20,710 --> 00:38:22,760
I also find it strange.

757
00:38:23,230 --> 00:38:24,190
How could he

758
00:38:24,190 --> 00:38:25,630
be so talented?

759
00:38:27,430 --> 00:38:28,280
Fan Xian,

760
00:38:30,630 --> 00:38:32,040
do you have anything to say?

761
00:38:32,870 --> 00:38:34,120
Master Zhuang can say

762
00:38:34,120 --> 00:38:34,910
whatever he likes.

763
00:38:34,910 --> 00:38:36,910
After all, highly respected as Master Zhuang,

764
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:39,320
what he says counts even if he has no proof.

765
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:40,630
Your Majesty,

766
00:38:40,910 --> 00:38:42,360
I can prove that

767
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:43,470
Fan Xian wrote the poem at the poetry gathering

768
00:38:43,560 --> 00:38:45,190
held in Prince Jing's mansion.

769
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:47,600
Guo Baokun, the Imperial Compiler

770
00:38:47,600 --> 00:38:48,710
was also there.

771
00:38:48,710 --> 00:38:50,470
He can be a witness.

772
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:52,870
Is Guo Baokun here?

773
00:38:52,910 --> 00:38:53,710
Yes, Your Majesty.

774
00:39:01,120 --> 00:39:03,470
Did Fan Xian write the poem?

775
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:07,670
Yes.

776
00:39:08,430 --> 00:39:09,230
In this case,

777
00:39:09,520 --> 00:39:11,600
Master Zhuang is trying to frame Fan Xian up on purpose.

778
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,840
He might be misled by others

779
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:16,470
to form such a misunderstanding.

780
00:39:22,560 --> 00:39:23,870
What a coincidence!

781
00:39:24,280 --> 00:39:25,710
The latter four lines of the poem

782
00:39:26,430 --> 00:39:27,710
were written by my teacher

783
00:39:28,080 --> 00:39:29,800
when he was visiting Tingzhou.

784
00:39:30,670 --> 00:39:33,630
It should to be a good thing to see

785
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:36,840
such wonderful lines reappearing in the world.

786
00:39:37,230 --> 00:39:38,360
But Mr. Fan

787
00:39:38,760 --> 00:39:40,710
actually made a name with other's poem.

788
00:39:42,150 --> 00:39:43,630
Is that appropriate?

789
00:39:46,600 --> 00:39:50,470
For scholars, morality is more important than talent.

790
00:39:53,040 --> 00:39:54,870
The first four lines of the poem

791
00:39:55,360 --> 00:39:57,190
are remarkable.

792
00:39:58,280 --> 00:40:00,120
Mr. Fan is definitely talented.

793
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:03,870
But why does he have to be so greedy

794
00:40:03,870 --> 00:40:05,800
as to make a name

795
00:40:06,150 --> 00:40:07,950
with other's work.

796
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:11,800
I was hesitant about

797
00:40:13,280 --> 00:40:14,910
telling the truth.

798
00:40:16,040 --> 00:40:17,670
But after careful thinking,

799
00:40:19,910 --> 00:40:21,430
I feel that by telling the truth,

800
00:40:22,040 --> 00:40:23,430
I might help Mr. Fan

801
00:40:23,430 --> 00:40:24,870
correct his mistake.

802
00:40:25,520 --> 00:40:28,840
There's no making without breaking.

803
00:40:29,040 --> 00:40:32,000
He can focus on moral cultivation in future.

804
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:33,390
Mr. Fan,

805
00:40:35,190 --> 00:40:36,150
I told the truth

806
00:40:36,150 --> 00:40:37,560
because I cherish your talents.

807
00:40:38,080 --> 00:40:39,560
I mean no harm.

808
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:42,950
Please be introspective.

809
00:40:43,710 --> 00:40:44,630
Fan Xian,

810
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:46,670
feel free to speak your mind.

811
00:40:47,600 --> 00:40:48,630
Master Zhuang,

812
00:40:50,080 --> 00:40:51,630
is your teacher surnamed Du?

813
00:40:52,560 --> 00:40:54,390
No.

814
00:40:55,910 --> 00:40:57,000
Never mind.

815
00:40:58,600 --> 00:41:00,040
Master Zhuang is known for

816
00:41:00,040 --> 00:41:01,360
respecting teachers and honoring truth,

817
00:41:01,870 --> 00:41:03,630
I suppose he won't use his teacher's reputation

818
00:41:03,630 --> 00:41:04,670
to frame up an innocent man.

819
00:41:06,120 --> 00:41:07,520
But men are hard to predict.

820
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:11,280
He might feel unhappy

821
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:14,430
seeing a young man rising to his fame

822
00:41:15,040 --> 00:41:17,950
and make all this up to destroy his future.

823
00:41:18,800 --> 00:41:19,630
Your Highness,

824
00:41:20,470 --> 00:41:21,840
are you suspecting me of framing this young man up

825
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:24,670
at the cost of my teacher's reputation?

826
00:41:25,040 --> 00:41:25,840
I dare not.

827
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:28,760
It's just that unlike Beiqi,

828
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:31,000
Nanqing emphasizes laws.

829
00:41:31,670 --> 00:41:33,840
If you want to accuse someone,

830
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:35,760
words alone

831
00:41:36,150 --> 00:41:37,560
won't be enough.

832
00:41:40,230 --> 00:41:42,600
Your Highness, you've made a point.

833
00:41:49,600 --> 00:41:52,430
Look, it was written by my teacher

834
00:41:52,560 --> 00:41:53,760
back then.

835
00:41:56,630 --> 00:41:58,120
Could it be

836
00:41:58,560 --> 00:41:59,760
the proof?

837
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:16,470
The lines are exactly the same.

838
00:42:55,060 --> 00:42:58,380
In the river of history,

839
00:42:58,660 --> 00:43:01,580
time goes round and round.

840
00:43:04,940 --> 00:43:07,940
Memories about the former and present lives

841
00:43:08,300 --> 00:43:11,820
join each other in an endless way.

842
00:43:14,260 --> 00:43:16,420
In the long drunken Milky Way,

843
00:43:16,900 --> 00:43:19,140
one season follows another in a flash,

844
00:43:19,140 --> 00:43:21,340
and the wild geese are flying south.

845
00:43:21,660 --> 00:43:23,260
I just can't give up

